Class AddMoodEventViewModel

java.lang.Object
androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
com.example.justacupofjavapersonal.ui.addmoodfragment.AddMoodEventViewModel
public class AddMoodEventViewModel extends androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
ViewModel class for the AddMoodEventFragment. This class holds the selected date and the list of moods that the user has selected.
